---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import CTAButton from '../../../components/CTAButton.astro';
import { COMPANY_INFO } from '../../../utils/constants';

const lang = 'ms';
const post = {
  title: 'Pembiayaan Peralatan Berat - 0% Deposit Malaysia 2026',
  slug: 'pembiayaan-peralatan-berat-0-deposit-malaysia-2026',
  excerpt: 'Dapatkan pembiayaan peralatan berat dengan 0% deposit di Malaysia. Bank tawarkan 90% pembiayaan sahaja dengan had umur 5 tahun. Ing Heng tawarkan 100% pinjaman penuh tanpa had umur untuk eskavator, jentolak, dan jentera berat lain.',
  date: '2026-01-01',
  author: 'Pasukan Ing Heng Credit',
  readTime: 4,
  category: 'Pembiayaan Peralatan Berat',
  image: '/images/blog/excavator-financing.jpg'
};

const keywords = ['pembiayaan peralatan berat', 'pembiayaan jentera', '0% deposit', 'eskavator', 'jentolak'];
const breadcrumbItems = [
  { label: 'Utama', href: '/ms' },
  { label: 'Blog', href: '/ms/blog' },
  { label: post.title, href: `/ms/blog/${post.slug}` }
];
---

<BaseLayout title={post.title} description={post.excerpt} lang={lang} keywords={keywords}>
  <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "BlogPosting",
      "headline": post.title,
      "description": post.excerpt,
      "datePublished": post.date,
      "author": { "@type": "Organization", "name": post.author },
      "publisher": {
        "@type": "Organization",
        "name": "Ing Heng Credit & Leasing Sdn Bhd",
        "logo": {
          "@type": "ImageObject",
          "url": "https://inghengcredit.com/logo.png"
        }
      }
    }
  </script>

  <Breadcrumbs items={breadcrumbItems} />

  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <header class="mb-8">
      <span class="text-sm font-semibold" style="color: #D4A574;">Pembiayaan Peralatan Berat</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-2" style="color: #2D1810; font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase;">{post.title}</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">{post.excerpt}</p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">
        <span>{post.author}</span>
        <span>•</span>
        <time>{new Date(post.date).toLocaleDateString('ms-MY', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</time>
        <span>•</span>
        <span>{post.readTime} min bacaan</span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h2>0% Deposit - Simpan Cash Anda</h2>

      <p>Pembiayaan peralatan berat dengan 0% deposit bukan lagi mimpi. Di Ing Heng Credit, kami tawarkan 100% pinjaman penuh untuk semua jenis jentera berat.</p>

      <p>Bank di Malaysia biasanya minta 10-20% deposit. Untuk eskavator RM50,000, anda perlu bayar RM5,000-RM10,000 di muka. Itu banyak wang!</p>

      <h2>Masalah Dengan Bank</h2>

      <p>Bank mempunyai limit yang ketat untuk pembiayaan peralatan berat:</p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Down payment:</strong> 10-20% wajib</li>
        <li><strong>Pembiayaan:</strong> Hanya 90% dari harga</li>
        <li><strong>Had umur:</strong> 5 tahun maksimum</li>
        <li><strong>Rate:</strong> 4.6% - 6.0% setahun</li>
      </ul>

      <p>Banyak kontraktor kecil ditolak oleh bank. Syarat terlalu ketat.</p>

      <h2>Penyelesaian Ing Heng</h2>

      <p>Kami tawarkan pembiayaan peralatan berat yang lebih fleksibel:</p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Down payment:</strong> 0%</li>
        <li><strong>Pembiayaan:</strong> 100% pinjaman penuh</li>
        <li><strong>Had umur:</strong> Tiada had</li>
        <li><strong>Rate:</strong> Kompetitif</li>
        <li><strong>Kelulusan:</strong> 24-48 jam</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Jadual Perbandingan</h2>

      <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 2rem 0;">
        <thead>
          <tr style="background: #2D1810; color: white;">
            <th style="padding: 1rem; text-align: left;">Ciri-ciri</th>
            <th style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center;">Bank</th>
            <th style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center;">Ing Heng</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
            <td style="padding: 1rem;"><strong>Down Payment</strong></td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center;">10-20%</td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center;"><strong>0%</strong></td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; background: #f9fafb;">
            <td style="padding: 1rem;"><strong>Pinjaman</strong></td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center;">90%</td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center;"><strong>100%</strong></td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
            <td style="padding: 1rem;"><strong>Had Umur</strong></td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center;">5 tahun</td>
            <td style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center;"><strong>Tiada had</strong></td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <h2>Contoh Sebenar</h2>

      <p><strong>Equipment:</strong> Jentolak CAT terpakai - RM50,000</p>

      <p><strong>Bank:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Deposit (10%): RM5,000</li>
        <li>Pinjaman: RM45,000</li>
        <li>Kelulusan: 2-4 minggu</li>
      </ul>

      <p><strong>Ing Heng:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Deposit (0%): <strong>RM0</strong></li>
        <li>Pinjaman: <strong>RM50,000</strong></li>
        <li>Kelulusan: 24-48 jam</li>
      </ul>

      <p><strong>Jimat:</strong> RM5,000 untuk operasi lain!</p>

      <h2>Jenis Peralatan Berat Kami Biayai</h2>

      <p>Kami biayai semua jenis peralatan berat:</p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Eskavator:</strong> Komatsu, CAT, Kubota, Hitachi</li>
        <li><strong>Jentolak:</strong> CAT, Komatsu</li>
        <li><strong>Kren:</strong> Mobile crane, tower crane</li>
        <li><strong>Loader:</strong> Wheel loader, backhoe</li>
        <li><strong>Lori:</strong> Tipper, prime mover</li>
        <li><strong>Forklift:</strong> Semua kapasiti</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Hubungi Kami</h2>

      <p>Jangan biarkan deposit tinggi halang perniagaan anda. Dapatkan pembiayaan peralatan berat 0% deposit hari ini.</p>

      <div style="background: #F5F0E8; border-left: 4px solid #D4A574; padding: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0;">
        <h3 style="color: #2D1810; margin-top: 0;">Pembiayaan Peralatan Berat 0% Deposit</h3>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">Dapatkan kelulusan dalam 24-48 jam. WhatsApp kami untuk konsultasi percuma.</p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 0;"><strong>Hubungi:</strong> +60175700889 (WhatsApp) | 03-3324 8899 (Telefon)</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t">
      <CTAButton text="Dapatkan Pembiayaan" link={COMPANY_INFO.whatsapp.link} variant="accent" size="large" />
    </footer>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  h2 {
    color: #2D1810;
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 3px solid #D4A574;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  p {
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #374151;
  }

  strong {
    color: #2D1810;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding-left: 0;
  }

  li {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #374151;
  }

  li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #D4A574;
    font-weight: bold;
  }
</style>
